articles.description: The Swedish internet personality, 33, who's real name is Felix Arvid Ulf Kjellberg, took to Youtube to announce the news on Sunday with over 680,000 views in just one hour.
articles.content:
YouTuber PewDiePie has announced he is expecting his first child with Italian wife Marzia Kjellberg.
